div.div: End of stage 1. This figure shows that the new Book with a new BookAuthor
linking to the Book has a State of Detached, and the existing Author, which was read in
from the database, has a State of Unchanged. The figure also shows the two navigational
links that the code set up to link the Book entity to the Author entity. Finally, the primary
and foreign keys of the Book and BookAuthor are unset—that is, zero—whereas the Author
entity has an existing primary key (123) because it is already in the database.
